    Vehicle Info Required to Guarantee Fit:
    Select a vehicle for Exact Fit

    In California, used cores can be returned to a NAPA Auto Parts store within 45 days to receive a refund. Please bring your receipt or order confirmation for the newly purchased replacement part. NAPA will also accept for recycling (not refund of core deposit) batteries that were NOT purchased at NAPA - up to 6 per day. For more information, visit What Is A Core?

    Features & Benefits

    Warranty :Standard : 36 Months Free Replacement

    Meets OEM AGM Standards For An Exact Fit Replacement Including Power, Configuration, & Venting Requirements. Maintenance-Free Delivers Maximum Starting Power without Adding Water. Deep Pocket Envelope Separators Prevent Shorts For More Power.


    • OE Part Number: GJ5Z-7443150, GJ5Z7443150.
    • Fitment: The liftgate lock actuator is compatible for Ford Escape 2017-2019.
    • Material: The liftgate lock actuator is made of premium iron material, sturdy, with excellent performance and long-lasting durability.
    • Position: Located inside the rear liftgate door, the power door lock actuator controls the locks on your vehicle.
    • Easy to install: Perfect match for the original vehicle. The liftgate lock actuator meets or exceeds OE standards, dependable to use.
